                        <h1>What is a troy ounce?</h1>
                        <div>
                           =20
<p>A&nbsp;troy ounce&nbsp;is a system of weights used for precious metals a=
nd gems, based on a pound of 12 ounces as opposed to the traditional 16.</p=
>
<p>A troy ounce is 31.1034768 grams or 0.0311034768 kilograms.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>


